Description: # Opsview Python REST API client
        
        https://github.com/pschmitt/python-opsview
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```bash
        pip install opsview
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```python
        from opsview import Opsview
        o = Opsview(
            'opsview.example.com',
            verify_ssl=True,
            username='pschmitt',
            password='MySecretPassw0rd'
        )
        ```
        
